text: Mursalimkino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Meshchegarovsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2,203 as of 2010. There are 43 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Maloyaz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Mursalimkino
